POST-INSTALL:

		* Copy the file "Xyeahconsole" to your home dir (with "."):
		$ cp /usr/share/yeahconsole/Xyeahconsole ~/.Xyeahconsole

		* Merge it with the system file:
		$ cd
		$ xrdb -merge .Xyeahconsole
		
		You can persist the change by adding the line to your ".xinitrc" file:
                xrdb -merge .Xyeahconsole
		
USAGE:

		* http://www.linux.com/feature/119067
		* Read the included "Readme" from the source 
